Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, have some rolled omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What? N-No, I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you a friend of Hayama's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What will you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe lunch set A.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I am Yoko Nishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Because my once wealthy father's company\Nwent bankrupt, I now must live as a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,--Futaba, what do you usually eat for breakfast?\N--I was able to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...two wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Plain rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko, have some rolled omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:31.11,Main,,0,0,0,,What? N-No, I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,But, there will be less for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But, then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This is way too polite! Relax a little! Re-lax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! Like, we should call each other\Nby nicknames and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause we're friends! 'Cause we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Have we been friends this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, we haven't been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Gosh, we're just teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,A cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,T-Too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"Nothing Good for You Is Tasty"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter widdle kitty? Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama looks quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She does like cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just cats. I like dogs, birds, cows,\Nand horses, too! I love them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my dream to buy an island\Nand build Hayama Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,How grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Unexpected from her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph, is that how you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you keep pets at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a cat named "Bel."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,A cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,My family named her, though.\NShe's called "Beelzebub" or "Bel" for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Beelze--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Beelzebub! A prince of demons.\NAlso known as "Lord of the Flies."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,"Demon"\NA-A demon who takes the form of fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She was swarming with flies\Nwhen we took her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So we named her "Bel."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you have a minute, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, can you hand\Nthese out before the next class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,--Okay.\N--Can you also collect the homework notebooks during break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,--Man, that's a lot of worksheets!\N--How could I be thinking that Hayama is a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,She is such a good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Being class representative seems difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't really want to be class\Nrepresentative, but they insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, why didn't you refuse if you dislike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like having to do random duties,\Nbut it'll look good on my resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Class Rankings"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Shucks, I tried really hard this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"10th Selina Nishiyama"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nishiyama!\NYou're tenth in our grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And what about Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't say it! I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"4th Teru Hayama"\NAh, don't say it! I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:40.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't say it! I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right! Grades aren't everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,This is higher than your rank in middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a huge improvement already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama is so annoying.\NShe's always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be class representative, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, right? It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,They randomly chose her just because\Nshe {\i1}looks {\i0}like a class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't random. It was part of her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Haya... ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama had a "talk" with her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,She called me out for being "full of myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,--What's going on?\N--Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,She's crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Do people actually say that in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she {\i1}is {\i0}a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,"Quadratic Equation"          "May 9th"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,"Quadratic Equation"          "May 9th"\NSo, what if you apply this formula to this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what if you apply this formula to this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Todoroki, come up and try the first problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, get those legs moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:07:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, they're timing us for this? Why-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama! She's beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Or not. I'm about to lap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Run like you mean it,\Nor it's another lap for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything. I can't\Ntalk back to a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--I-I'm gonna die.\N--You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:32.66,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I be? She was trying to run us to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So even the great Hayama\Nhas a weakness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,--Nishiyama.\N--What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mind her, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,The poor thing. She looks down on people over\Nsuch small things. We should be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling "poor thing"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And you are {\i1}not {\i0}small.\NYou have a great figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,--W-Well, I do make sure to do\Nexercises and have balanced meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,--Beanpole.\N--W-Well, I do make sure to do exercises and have balanced meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--W-Well, I do make sure to do exercises and have balanced meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That's tough. You have to be careful\Nof what you eat or your weight fluctuates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You're still young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's totally wrong! Why are you\Nalways making a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You're so mean. That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Bye!\N--See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I still feel nauseated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You really dislike running, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Not running specifically,\Nbut I don't have stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm running on empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're definitely not running on empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,"Please take care of us."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Please take care of us."\NOh my, have they been abandoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,T-To think such young kittens have\Nbeen abandoned... It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What in the world were they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama actually has a gentle spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"Please take care of us."\NHayama actually has a gentle spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Please take care of us."\N"Please take care of us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show you who can take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever abandoned you, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the voice of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I found homes for two kittens,\Nbut there's one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It would be a struggle, but I can house it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.15,Main,,0,0,0,,First, I will find a property that allows pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the first step?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are any cat-lovers around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama used to have a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A cat? I did have one,\Nbut it died three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Your family had that cat since before you\Nwere born, right? You really loved it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop saying unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is {\i0}worth in the existence\Nof someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,So there wasn't any before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I actually took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, there was no other choice.\NNobody else could take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't like the fact that it\Nwas from Hayama, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You need a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,One that will give you a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Remember how I wanted\Nto make nicknames for all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. A nickname!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We need nicknames to become true friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't {\i1}have {\i0}to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama, Futaba! Please, give me\Na splendid nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yokoppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Not approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no, they are unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Something more lovely, noble,\Nand intellectual would serve better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Former Rich Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,As I was saying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Please address Miss Yoko as "Miss Yoko."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You appeared without a sound, so I thought\Nyou were someone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,If you please, address Miss Yoko as "Miss Yoko."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,This was not what I imagined\Nmy nickname to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, so Miss Yoko is "Miss Yoko." Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's Hayama's first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Futaba Odagiri. Miss Yoko is\NYoko Nishikawa. What's your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't this nice? It's so fun to eat outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! Tell us your first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's your first name? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, what's your next class?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, why won't you tell us?\NWhat's your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Te...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru. That's my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru! Miss Teru! Terumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't keep saying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with it. It's cute. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is quite a lovely name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Terurin... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, I don't have chopsticks in my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You can just get disposable ones\Nat the school store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! I knew I could ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so smart. I didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you a friend of Hayama's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not her friend. I'm her older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Her sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,She is Hayama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A demon and an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oy, oy! It's past April Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kou, Teru's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Wait here for a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, take one. I made them from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh no...\N--Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh...\N--I'll try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's full of nutrients!\NHomemade fermented bean candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Fermented bean?!\N--Yoko, I heard that you only eat bread crusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru is all black on the inside, but don't worry\Nabout that and get along with her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,She can be airheaded, so she'll say and do\Ninteresting things without meaning harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Airhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh. Lunch will end if you don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm going to try out\Nnew ingredients next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still early, Bel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the weekend. Let me sleep in a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,B-Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:11.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make a breakfast drink for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Special garlic banana milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw. Then, I'll give some special\Ngarlic banana milk to Bel instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I told her not to put garlic in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:36.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, you'll come grocery shopping\Nwith me today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Maekawa Fruits & Vegetables"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Maekawa Fruits & Vegetables"\NIt's been a while since we've gone out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've gone out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So, what do we need to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Books and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Books?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy a cookbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,And a photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Photo album?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you two up two? Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's been a very long time\Nsince I've gone out with Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You two sure do get along!\NI'm an only child, so I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Only when she's not trying to poison me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you shopping, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, to get some giblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll buy some giblets, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Big Sis, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Super Daimaru"              "Meat Fish Vegetables"\NOh, Big Sis, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Super Daimaru"              "Meat Fish Vegetables"\NGiblets, Chinese yam, okra, and {\i1}mulukhiyah{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"Spring Sale!"\NGiblets, Chinese yam, okra, and {\i1}mulukhiyah{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"Spring Sale!"\Nall mixed together to make a candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:39.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"Chinese yam, Okra, {\i1}Mulukhiyah, {\i0}Cookbook, Photo album"\Nall mixed together to make a candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Blegh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you obsessed with health foods?\NAnd then making candy out of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,They're easier to eat in candy form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's flash sale is mayonnaise! 500 grams\Nfor 98 yen! Limit one bottle per person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sale?\N--Don't miss your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"Today's Special Sale!"\N--Don't miss your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mayonnaise"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,In getting the special-sale mayonnaise\Nthat is limited to one per person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. So, you and your sister\Nare out grocery shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"Raffle Ticket"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,However, are you sure about this?\NCan I really take these raffle tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course. We got a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Win every time! Fifth place prize is\Npocket tissue! Fourth place is a coffee set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Third place is new crop rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Central Shopping Arcade"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Arcade Raffle"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"Arcade Raffle"\NFifth place prize of pocket tissue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Arcade Raffle"\NFourth place, coffee set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Arcade Raffle"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"Koshihikari Rice"\NThird place, the great new crop rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Koshihikari Rice"\NAn unselfish win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Koshihikari Rice"\NAck! I can't believe Hayama won when I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"Koshihikari Rice"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Third place, New Crop Rice"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Second Place, Halogen Heater"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"First Place, One Night Hot Springs Vacation"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She has pretty good luck with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not just "pretty good"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,She also got the bathhouse tickets from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't carry all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Yoko and Futaba\Ntook the heavy things for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give the hot springs vacation\Nto Mom and Dad and--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh no!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot to go to the bookstore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you buy a cookbook,\Nyou'll put other ingredients in anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And... a photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,A photo album?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,There were lots of photos in the closet.\NPhotos from when we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:20:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis! You'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'm a good climber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give the pretty butterfly to Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch! I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You used to get sick and get hurt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty healthy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't take it for granted. Make sure\Nyou get all your nutrients regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she always nagging about nutrients...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try my best at cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...because she's worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,She says it's a thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,They're rice balls! With liver,\Nwhite roe, and bitter melon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Mixed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But, where's all the stuff you bought yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is not a matter\Nof if it's healthy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But Hayama's sister went out of her way to make\Nthem for us. It's {\i1}food {\i0}that she made for... us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,--She's eating it!\N--Miss Yoko is actually a brave hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, do not allow Miss Yoko\Nto consume strange foods!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, you don't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even if this is your\Nrare chance to eat liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't encourage her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing good for you is tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't encourage her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is\Nso entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Money..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't say here"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We each have our own happiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's enjoy life as much as we want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's crazy and messy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's the rock scissors parade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the three of us gather{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For rock, paper, scissors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll tie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it'll never end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parade's started, and you have to join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer to one times three{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to know, then come here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Being rich is not all that wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,But that does not mean my current life is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be green after eating\Na strange rice ball either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But, all of us being able to eat the rice balls\Nthat Hayama's sister made for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,...makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Your real thoughts are leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next time: A Taste of Maid"\NMiss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Next time: A Taste of Maid"
